title: 151: The Ice Cream Haul Episode (Sponsored by Enlightened)
itunes:title: The Ice Cream Haul Episode (Sponsored by Enlightened)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa and the crew are taste-testing some killer frozen (and non-frozen) finds from our friends & partners at Enlightened! Tasty treats like low-sugar fruit bars, new LIGHT pints of ice cream, out-of-this-world dough bites, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, a new sugar-free cone that YOU MUST BUY ASAP! So stop what you’re doing right now, push play, and then when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the items mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: It’s hot out there, so you’re in the right place! We have an Ice Cream Haul to cool you down on Chew the Right Thing!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
